    <refsect1 xml:id="description"><title>Description</title>
        <para>
            <function>imageSize</function> returns the dimensions of the image bound to <parameter>image</parameter>.
            The components in the return value are filled in,
            in order, with the width, height and depth of the image. For the array forms, the last component of the
            return value is the number of layers in the texture array.
        </para>
    </refsect1>
